desc_long								关于这款游戏							Match 3 Revolution” is an original physics Match 3/ Marble Popper game. Its main features are:-	Create sets of at least 3 touching balls of the same color.-	100 Levels of Unique Gameplay.-	Original game modes: click a ball, draw a line, drop a ball and play pinball.-	Supercharge with combos.-	A lot of power-ups (electroball, fireball, megabomb, fusionball, missiles,…).-	Top 50 Online World Ranking in every level.-	Original music.						
