desc_short	-----								"Match 3 Revolution” is an original physics match3/marble game with 100 game levels. Create sets of at least 3 touching balls of the same color. Original game modes, supercharge with combos, a lot of power-ups (electroball, fireball, megabomb, fusionball, missiles,…) and a Top 50 Online World Ranking in every level.							
